File Version: 2012-11-01

Contact: Boris Hekele, hekele@parliamentwatch.org

This is a basic outline how to install this repo. Please get in touch with us when you have any problems regarding the install process. The software is currently under heavy developement and not free of bugs. A lot up feel good-functions are still missing at this point.
=======

SETUP
- install latest drush version
- Clone repo
- Install repo by running build.sh
- Clone multisite folder into sites directory

Basic Configuration
- Add your language. Please leave english as default system language.
- Translate all strings using the build-in interface

Import Data (example CSVs are not ready yet)
- Fill up CSV to import MPs
- Fill up CSV to import committees
- Fill up CSV to import constituencies
- Fill up CSV to import a vote

Connect to moderation software
- Needs to be documented
